text: is a Japanese football player. She played for the Japan national team. ==Biography== Ueno was born in Matsudo on November 20, 1994. In 2013, she joined JEF United Chiba from Urawa Reds youth team. She won the Best Young Player award in the 2013 season. She played 132 matches until 2019. In 2020, she moved to Urawa Reds.
